    public class A16AlgebraRelation
extends BitSetAlgebraRelation<A16BaseRelation>
    The A16 Algebras of relations (see: Armen Inants, Jérôme Euzenat, Algebras of ontology alignment relations, Proc. ISWC, 2015). JEPD relations between classes, enventually empty, and individuals
